            <ab>Harsiesis, the emissary of the epimeletes for the estimate of sesame, to N.N. and the elders of the cultivators, greeting. As soon as you read my letter, repair quickly with no delay to Oxyrhyncha in order that we may ï¿½; and I have sent Ptolemaios ... (Addressed on the recto:) [To the cultivators] of Areos kome</ab>
